text: Northland College is the name of several learning institutions: ;Canada * Northlands College in Saskatchewan ;New Zealand * Northland College (Kaikohe), a small high school at Kaikohe in the far north of New Zealand ;United States of America * Northland College (Minnesota) in Minnesota, a Community and Technical college * Northland College (Wisconsin) in Ashland, Wisconsin, a small liberal arts college * Northland Baptist Bible College, a private college in Wisconsin (Not affiliated with Northland college in Ashland)
title: Northland College
